### ===========================
### AGRICULTEURS
### ===========================

@token = Bearer 

### Create Agriculteur
POST http://localhost:3000/agriculteurs
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
  "nom": "Ahmed El Fellah",
  "telephone": "+212600000001",
  "region": "Souss-Massa",
  "userId": 2
}

### Get All Agriculteurs
GET http://localhost:3000/agriculteurs
Authorization: {{token}}

### Get Agriculteur by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/agriculteurs/1
Authorization: {{token}}

### Get Agriculteur Parcelles
GET http://localhost:3000/agriculteurs/1/parcelles
Authorization: {{token}}

### Update Agriculteur
PUT http://localhost:3000/agriculteurs/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
  "nom": "Ahmed Updated",
  "telephone": "+212600000002",
  "region": "Marrakech-Safi"
}

### Delete Agriculteur
DELETE http://localhost:3000/agriculteurs/1
Authorization: {{token}}

